      <section class="article-section" id="problema">
        <SectionHeader number="01" kickerEs="Del archivo al producto de datos" kickerEn="From files to a data product" titleEs="El reto no era descargar información. Era preservar su significado." titleEn="The challenge was not downloading information. It was preserving meaning." introEs="SIMEM publica datos valiosos, pero analizarlos juntos exige resolver granos, versiones, historia dimensional y cortes temporales diferentes." introEn="SIMEM publishes valuable data, but analyzing it together requires resolving grains, versions, dimensional history and different temporal cutoffs." />
        <div class="problem-grid">
          <div class="prose">
            <p class="lede lang-es">Conectar Power BI directamente a los archivos habría trasladado la complejidad al dashboard: doble conteo por versiones TX, joins que pierden plantas y comparaciones entre fuentes con fechas de actualización distintas.</p>
            <p class="lede lang-en">Connecting Power BI directly to the files would have moved complexity into the dashboard: TX-version double counting, joins that lose plants, and comparisons across sources with different update dates.</p>
            <p class="lang-es">El objetivo del MVP fue construir una cadena reproducible que conservara el dato recibido, añadiera trazabilidad, lo transformara con reglas explícitas y lo publicara mediante contratos estables. Por eso la solución se planteó como un <strong>producto de datos</strong>, no como un conjunto de notebooks aislados.</p>
            <p class="lang-en">The MVP objective was to build a reproducible chain that preserves the received data, adds lineage, transforms it through explicit rules and publishes it through stable contracts. The solution was therefore designed as a <strong>data product</strong>, not a collection of isolated notebooks.</p>
            <div class="callout"><strong><span class="lang-es">Objetivo funcional</span><span class="lang-en">Functional objective</span></strong><span class="lang-es">Integrar fuentes energéticas públicas en Databricks, procesarlas con arquitectura Medallion, modelarlas dimensionalmente y exponer vistas confiables para analítica.</span><span class="lang-en">Integrate public energy sources in Databricks, process them with a Medallion architecture, model them dimensionally and expose trusted analytical views.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-cards">
            <article class="problem-card"><span class="problem-card__number" aria-hidden="true">01</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Granos diferentes</span><span class="lang-en">Different grains</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Generación, disponibilidad y precio son horarios; energía embalsada y maestros tienen otra frecuencia.</span><span class="lang-en">Generation, availability and price are hourly; stored energy and master data have other frequencies.</span></p></article>
            <article class="problem-card"><span class="problem-card__number" aria-hidden="true">02</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Revisiones TX</span><span class="lang-en">TX revisions</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Varias filas pueden representar estados sucesivos de una misma medición y no eventos distintos.</span><span class="lang-en">Several rows may represent successive states of the same measurement rather than different events.</span></p></article>
            <article class="problem-card"><span class="problem-card__number" aria-hidden="true">03</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Historia de dimensiones</span><span class="lang-en">Dimensional history</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Plantas y agentes cambian de atributos, nombre, clasificación o capacidad a lo largo del tiempo.</span><span class="lang-en">Plants and agents change attributes, names, classification or capacity over time.</span></p></article>
            <article class="problem-card"><span class="problem-card__number" aria-hidden="true">04</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Frescura desalineada</span><span class="lang-en">Misaligned freshness</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Las fuentes no terminan en la misma fecha; un KPI combinado necesita un corte común explícito.</span><span class="lang-en">Sources do not end on the same date; combined KPIs need an explicit common cutoff.</span></p></article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="article-section article-section--tint" id="fuentes">
        <SectionHeader number="02" kickerEs="Dominio y procedencia" kickerEn="Domain and provenance" titleEs="Nueve fuentes para observar el sistema energético desde varias perspectivas." titleEn="Nine sources to observe the energy system from multiple perspectives." introEs="Cada fuente resuelve una pregunta distinta. La arquitectura evita forzarlas a compartir una estructura que no les corresponde." introEn="Each source answers a different question. The architecture avoids forcing them into a structure that does not fit their nature." />
        <div class="source-toolbar" role="group" aria-label="Filtrar fuentes">
          <span><span class="lang-es">Explorar por dominio</span><span class="lang-en">Explore by domain</span></span>
          <div>
            <button class="source-filter is-active" type="button" data-source-filter="all"><span class="lang-es">Todos</span><span class="lang-en">All</span> <b>9</b></button>
            <button class="source-filter" type="button" data-source-filter="operation"><span class="lang-es">Operación</span><span class="lang-en">Operations</span> <b>4</b></button>
            <button class="source-filter" type="button" data-source-filter="market"><span class="lang-es">Mercado</span><span class="lang-en">Market</span> <b>2</b></button>
            <button class="source-filter" type="button" data-source-filter="master"><span class="lang-es">Maestros</span><span class="lang-en">Masters</span> <b>3</b></button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="source-grid">
          <article class="source-card" data-source-category="operation"><span class="source-card__icon">G</span><code>055A4D · GREAL</code><h3><span class="lang-es">Generación real</span><span class="lang-en">Actual generation</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Medición horaria por planta, agente y versión.</span><span class="lang-en">Hourly measurement by plant, agent and version.</span></p><small>hour · plant · agent · TX</small></article>
          <article class="source-card" data-source-category="operation"><span class="source-card__icon">D</span><code>DISPREAL</code><h3><span class="lang-es">Disponibilidad de plantas</span><span class="lang-en">Plant availability</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Capacidad disponible reportada por recurso y hora.</span><span class="lang-en">Available capacity reported by resource and hour.</span></p><small>hour · plant</small></article>
          <article class="source-card" data-source-category="market"><span class="source-card__icon">$</span><code>EC6945 · PB</code><h3><span class="lang-es">Precio de bolsa</span><span class="lang-en">Spot price</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Precio nacional, internacional y TIE por periodo.</span><span class="lang-en">National, international and TIE price by period.</span></p><small>hour · market</small></article>
          <article class="source-card" data-source-category="market"><span class="source-card__icon">M</span><code>DEMREAL</code><h3><span class="lang-es">Demanda real</span><span class="lang-en">Actual demand</span></h3><p><span class="lang-es">Consumo horario por agente y tipo de mercado.</span><span class="lang-en">Hourly consumption by agent and market type.</span></p><small>hour · agent · market</small></article>
