          <article class="eda-lane reveal"><div class="eda-lane__top"><span class="eda-lane__number" aria-hidden="true">02</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Validez y dominios</span><span class="lang-en">Validity and domains</span></h3></div><p><span class="lang-es">Conversión de fechas y medidas, unidades, duración, variables, mercados y versiones permitidas.</span><span class="lang-en">Date and measure conversion, units, duration, variables, markets and allowed versions.</span></p></article>
          <article class="eda-lane reveal"><div class="eda-lane__top"><span class="eda-lane__number" aria-hidden="true">03</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Unicidad y revisiones</span><span class="lang-en">Uniqueness and revisions</span></h3></div><p><span class="lang-es">Duplicados exactos, conflictos dentro de la misma versión y multiplicidad entre versiones TX.</span><span class="lang-en">Exact duplicates, conflicts within the same version and multiplicity across TX versions.</span></p></article>
