          <article class="eda-lane reveal"><div class="eda-lane__top"><span class="eda-lane__number" aria-hidden="true">05</span><h3><span class="lang-es">Coherencia operativa</span><span class="lang-en">Operational coherence</span></h3></div><p><span class="lang-es">Generación frente a disponibilidad, capacidad y demanda, sin convertir señales en errores confirmados.</span><span class="lang-en">Generation versus availability, capacity and demand, without turning signals into confirmed errors.</span></p></article>
